---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="Ata Onat">
  <section class="intro">
    <h1>Hi, I'm Ata.</h1>
    <p>
      I spent years in private equity — first in New York, then in Vietnam, then investing across
      emerging and developed markets for a fund based in Singapore. I liked the realism of investing,
      but I always had this side of me that wanted to build something and be a little unrealistic.
    </p>
    <p>
      Now I'm doing that. Currently building <a href="https://analystai.co" target="_blank">AnalystAI</a>,
      an AI startup. I also co-founded
      <a href="https://siminacollective.com" target="_blank">Simina Collective</a>,
      a hand-knit clothing brand, with my mom.
    </p>
    <p>
      I write about history, culture, startups, investing, and whatever else is on my mind.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="recent">
    <h2>Recent writing</h2>
    <ul class="article-list">
      <li>
        <a href="/writing/capital-is-not-conviction">Capital Is Not Conviction</a>
        <span class="date">Apr 2026</span>
      </li>
      <li>
        <a href="/writing/the-organizing-instinct">The Organizing Instinct</a>
        <span class="date">Apr 2026</span>
      </li>
      <li>
        <a href="/writing/investors-should-play-with-ai">If You're an Investor, You Should Play with AI</a>
        <span class="date">Apr 2026</span>
      </li>
      <li>
        <a href="/writing/the-efficiency-paradox">The Efficiency Paradox</a>
        <span class="date">Apr 2026</span>
      </li>
      <li>
        <a href="/writing/coconut-kingdom-and-the-branding-problem">The Coconut Kingdom and the Branding Problem</a>
        <span class="date">Apr 2026</span>
      </li>
      <li>
        <a href="/writing/why-i-write">Why I Write</a>
        <span class="date">Apr 2026</span>
      </li>
    </ul>
    <p class="more"><a href="/writing">All writing &rarr;</a></p>
  </section>
</Base>

<style>
  .intro {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .intro p {
    color: #444;
  }

  .recent h2 {
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 500;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    color: #999;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .article-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .article-list li {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: 1rem;
    padding: 0.6rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
  }

  .article-list a {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .article-list a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-decoration-color: #ccc;
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .article-list li {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 0.2rem;
    }
  }

  .more {
    margin-top: 1rem;
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
  }

  .more a {
    color: #666;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .more a:hover {
    color: #1a1a1a;
  }
</style>
